# Cloudflare Pages redirects for Narramorph (Batch 8.4).
#
# Canonical host: narramorph.com (apex). www redirects to apex, preserving the path
# (301). If you prefer www as canonical, swap the two hostnames below.
#
# The app is hash-routed (#/passage/:id), so all real navigation is under "/",
# which serves index.html. Genuinely unknown paths fall through to the branded
# 404.html — no SPA rewrite is needed.
https://www.narramorph.com/* https://narramorph.com/:splat 301!
